    excerpt: "A comprehensive guide to the most powerful AgencyOS commands for marketing, sales, and content.",
    date: "Dec 18, 2024",
    category: "Tutorial",
    readTime: "12 min",
    featured: true,
    image: "ðŸ¤–"
  },
  {
    title: "The Affiliate Playbook: $5K/Month Passive Income",
    excerpt: "Step-by-step guide to building a passive income stream with PayPal-friendly affiliate programs.",
    date: "Dec 15, 2024",
    category: "Guide",
    readTime: "8 min",
    featured: false,
    image: "ðŸ’°"
  },
  {
    title: "From Freelancer to Agency Owner in 90 Days",
    excerpt: "The exact framework to transition from solo freelancer to running a profitable one-person agency.",
    date: "Dec 12, 2024",
    category: "Strategy",
    readTime: "10 min",
    featured: false,
    image: "ðŸš€"
  },
  {
